text: Thirtysomething is an American television series. Thirtysomething or 30-something may also refer to: * Thirty Something (Taiwanese TV series), a Taiwanese television series * Thirtysomething (age), a term of approximation denoting one who is, or who is believed to be, in one's thirties ==See also== * 30 Something, an album by Carter the Unstoppable Sex Machine * Twentysomething (disambiguation)
